+# In-Play Institutional++ Scorecard (96% target)
+
+Laser-focused reliability gates for the live CTMC quant lane.
+
+## Score
+
+```bash
+bash scripts/score_inplay_institutional.sh
+bash scripts/preflight_inplay.sh   # exit 0 pass | 1 warn | 2 fail
+```
+
+**Target:** `score_pct >= 96` → grade **A++** → `buyer_ready=true`
+
+## Gates (weighted)
+
+| Gate | Weight | Requirement |
+|------|--------|-------------|
+| `inplay_enabled` | 2.0 | `HIBS_INPLAY_ENABLED=1` |
+| `circuit_closed` | 2.0 | Circuit breaker not open |
+| `error_budget` | 2.0 | Tick error rate ≤ 5% |
+| `latency_slo` | 1.5 | p95 tick ≤ 500ms |
+| `live_confirm` | 2.0 | Live execute requires `CONFIRM_LIVE=YES` |
+| `no_blocking_issues` | 2.0 | Zero blocking config issues |
+| `rust_kernel` | 1.5 | Kernel built (or kernel disabled) |
+| `kelly_cap` | 1.5 | Kelly fraction ≤ 0.30 |
+| `worker_heartbeat` | 1.5 | Fresh if `HIBS_INPLAY_WORKER_REQUIRED=1` |
+| `archive_ticks` | 1.0 | Tick archive enabled |
+| `intensity_weights` | 1.0 | 13-feature weight vector resolved |
+| `var_suspend` | 1.0 | VAR suspension on |
+| `preflight_script` | 0.5 | `scripts/preflight_inplay.sh` exists |
+
+## Failsafe principles
+
+1. **Never crash the dashboard** — `safe_tick_fixture` / `safe_attach_to_fixture` catch all exceptions.
+2. **Circuit breaker** — 5 consecutive failures → 30s cooldown.
+3. **Probability validation** — sum-to-one renormalisation before attach.
+4. **Stale guard** — reject ticks older than `HIBS_INPLAY_MAX_TICK_AGE_SEC`.
+5. **Telemetry** — p95 latency + error rate on `/api/health` → `stack_ops.inplay`.
+
+## Health surfaces
+
+- `GET /api/inplay/readiness` — full scorecard + gates
+- `GET /api/inplay/probabilities` — includes `readiness` block
+- `GET /api/health` — `stack_ops.inplay` summary
+- `institutional_failsafe.failsafe_report()` — `inplay_lane` block
+
+## Production checklist
+
+```bash
+bash scripts/build_inplay_kernel.sh
+export HIBS_INPLAY_ENABLED=1
+export HIBS_INPLAY_ARCHIVE_TICKS=1
+export HIBS_INPLAY_KERNEL=1
+bash scripts/preflight_inplay.sh
+bash scripts/run_inplay_quant_worker.sh &
+bash scripts/score_inplay_institutional.sh
+```
+
+See also `docs/INPLAY_TRADING_ARCHITECTURE.md`.
